2. **`(?=.*(?<![a-zA-Z0-9])(IP_PATTERN)(?![a-zA-Z0-9]))`** — Lookahead asserting the line contains a valid IPv4 address (no leading zeros, octets 0-255) not preceded/followed by alphanumeric chars
